ai_summary.en: The broader crypto market is currently mired in 'Extreme Fear' with the BTC Fear & Greed Index at 20. Amidst this, institutional whales on Ethereum exhibit a cautious, near-neutral sentiment, marked by substantial stablecoin inflows and neutral large transfers. In stark contrast, retail and speculative money on Solana shows pronounced bearishness, evidenced by significant stablecoin outflows and consistently bearish top transfers. This divergence suggests institutional accumulation of stablecoins on ETH while retail capitulates on SOL, hinting at continued market caution and potential further consolidation until clear directional conviction emerges.
ai_summary.zh: 加密市场目前陷入‘极度恐惧’，比特币恐惧与贪婪指数为20。在此背景下，以太坊上的机构鲸鱼表现出谨慎的、接近中性的情绪，特点是大量的稳定币流入和中性的大额转账。与此形成鲜明对比的是，Solana上的散户和投机资金表现出明显的看跌情绪，大量稳定币流出和持续的看跌大额转账印证了这一点。这种分歧表明机构在ETH上积累稳定币，而散户在SOL上投降，预示着市场将继续保持谨慎，并可能在明确的方向性信念出现之前进一步盘整。
